      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;GitScribe&lt;/strong&gt; is a Go-based tool for automating high-quality Git commit messages using LLMs. This tool features &lt;strong&gt;zero-dependency Go architecture&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;context-aware intelligence&lt;/strong&gt;, and &lt;strong&gt;seamless integration with local LLMs like Ollama&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
